data.description: Charming 2nd floor condo now available in the desirable Brookwood subdivision!  Home features a 2-bedroom, 1 full bathroom with an open floor plan.  First thing that will catch your eye once you are upstairs is the beautiful wood burning stone fireplace that is from floor to ceiling!  Living room has vaulted ceilings with a skylight and sliding glass door that brings you to your own private balcony.  Down the hallway is the primary suite that features a substantial walk-in closet.  The hallway bathroom has a washer/dryer that are staying, and room connects to the primary suite to give more privacy.   Home has been very well-maintained over the years!  New gutters June 2023, newer windows, skylight and sliding door.  Front door has an August Smart Home lock that can connect to your app, Alexa and nest.   All light switches in living room and kitchen are compatible.  Home is close to all major roads & highways such as Easton Rd (Rt 611), Limekiln Pike and PA Turnpike - makes it perfect for commuters!
